    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Here are the instructions for using BMI calculator app</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <prereq class="- topic/section task/prereq " id="unique_1_Connect_42_prereq_t1j_wjd_zcc" nd:nd-id="prereq_t1j_wjd_zcc">You must know the measurement of your body weight and
